# index.json hashes every file by exact byte length + sha256, and ContentSync
# verifies those hashes on download. Force LF on text content so the hashes are
# byte-identical across Windows working trees, Linux CI, and GitHub raw/Release
# blobs — core.autocrlf=true otherwise smudges LF→CRLF locally and makes the
# freshness/verification non-deterministic per platform. (Moved here from the
# engine repo in Phase 4 — see docs/CONTENT-PCK-MIGRATION.md.)
*.import text eol=lf
*.json   text eol=lf
*.bbcode text eol=lf
*.svg    text eol=lf
*.md     text eol=lf
# Binary content — never convert (protects the content hashes).
*.png  binary
*.jpg  binary
*.jpeg binary
*.mp3  binary
*.glb  binary
